text = "Welcome to the new human colony on an alien planet.
Yes, you have officially left Earth and begun a new life far away from home.

A new life… full of paperwork.

As a foreigner here, you are required to complete all necessary documents. Be careful—mistakes
are not tolerated. The aliens are not fond of visitors, and if you annoy them enough, they won’t hesitate to
send youstraight back to Earth.

Please note that official working hours are strictly enforced. You are expected to process all documents
within your assigned shift. Overtime is neither guaranteed nor appreciated.

Fortunately, you were wise enough to bring your notes. You can access your notebook anytime by pressing [H].
It’s waiting for you on your desk.

Good luck—and enjoy the bureaucracy outside your home."
horizontal_alignment = 1
vertical_alignment = 1

